				\begin{document}$$C^{WK}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M16"><mml:msup><mml:mi>C</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">WK</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msup></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2023_5177_Article_IEq5.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the word-topic matrix, <inline-formula id="IEq6"><alternatives><tex-math id="M17">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
